{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2139693, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 415171, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "😅😅😅", "timestamp": 1627307377, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2139700, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 415171, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "面包和马戏，马戏要是能用来转移内部矛盾就更好了", "timestamp": 1627307410, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2139713, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 415171, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "竞技体育不是国家之间温和“秀肌肉”的途径吗", "timestamp": 1627307508, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2139731, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 415171, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不是脱离不了，是本来奥运就是政治的延伸", "timestamp": 1627307668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2139734, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 415171, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "奥运会本来就是国家间的比赛 谁怼着奥运会看竞技水平啊", "timestamp": 1627307699, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2139743, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 415171, "reply_to": 2139700, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 😅", "timestamp": 1627307772, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2139750, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 415171, "reply_to": 2139713, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 这种提法我觉得在当代并没有什么道理，赢了又怎么样？输了又怎么样？", "timestamp": 1627307805, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2139761, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 415171, "reply_to": 2139731, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 正好今天中美在谈判，美国会因为今天金牌数超过中国而在谈判中占据更优势的地位吗？所谓延伸究竟延伸在了哪里？", "timestamp": 1627307869, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2139820, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 415171, "reply_to": 2139750, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 孔雀的尾羽、狮子的鬃毛对个体的生存没有直接帮助，